{"tid":1025721,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］12月機票應該幾時買？","createTime":"2019-02-17T14:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T14:57:09.000Z","uid":214417,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6e4a235510a1512f5ca62b1ca84ccdf9f916f4","tid":1025721,"uid":214417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"之前第一次喺坐Jetstar 去東京，今年又想去多次東京，但望到12月尾機票好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Jetstar 個官網11月開始都未有得買，想問下通常幾時先買到？定喺無得買。<br />\n唔想坐uo<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教通常幾時去買旺季機票？因為暫時個時間想定12月尾"},{"pid":"4606f48f5546c1c2d2beba527b06f71e4b2c98cd","tid":1025721,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"航空業主要分夏季同冬季<br />\n分別係3月底同10月底開始<br />\n而家只係賣緊夏季既機票<br />\n根據以往經驗<br />\nJetstar Japan冬季起碼要6-7月先開始賣<br />\n(每間航空公司都唔同)"},{"pid":"23f4684f1ce3062a5cb3994e257757a3abffa627","tid":1025721,"uid":214417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4606f48f5546c1c2d2beba527b06f71e4b2c98cd","tid":1025721,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"航空業主要分夏季同冬季<br />\n分別係3月底同10月底開始<br />\n而家只係賣緊夏季既機票<br />\n根據以往經驗<br />\nJetstar Japan冬季起碼要6-7月先開始賣<br />\n(每間航空公司都唔同)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"Thanks ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想問下究竟機票應唔應該早買，我唔知道機票喺隨著供應需求而貴，定喺每年航空公司都會將旺季個價set高？即喺依家唔買，幾個月後佢會唔會推出優惠出售？"},{"pid":"2b49df3f51b25265bd0a7385d039e71a6405fc15","tid":1025721,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"a859ef4e89f1399200687d81980bac76fb4abcaa","tid":1025721,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"我係2018年3月，買到2019年2月ANA去東京的機票"},{"pid":"ba5bcb4f2578b45c6412dea03d14e068dc7a8547","tid":1025721,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit